title: iBass Magazine: Ron Carter Interview
description:
From his early days amid New York's free jazz boom in the 60s, to his famed partnership with Miles Davis, Ron Carter has performed with such an array of influential musicians that it's hard to describe his contribution to jazz.

Thanks to all at Ronnie Scott's Jazz Club, London. https://www.ronniescotts.co.uk
